Headline::::
Which uses the most energy: leaving the boiler on all the time, or using a timer?




DateTime::::2016-03-09T14:37:58+0000



<p>Am I saving energy by turning off the heat during the day and shivering? Or does it take more fuel to heat the house up again in the evening?<br/><em>Beth Noakes, London NW3</em></p>

<p><span class="bullet">•</span> Post your answers – and new questions – below, or email them to <a class="u-underline" data-component="in-body-link" data-link-name="in body link" href="mailto:nq@theguardian.com">nq@theguardian.com</a>. Please include name, address and phone number. <br/></p>




